            <h1>History</h1>
            <p>We’ve been passionate gamers since we have memory, but we’ve always had difficulties getting the best devices for our goals. High prices and low quality products that can’t satisfy our needs have marked Colombian gaming history. That’s why our project started a year ago with the idea of creating a Desktop Gaming PC offering a great balance in performance and price, using the latest technologies in the development process. This need was born when the market failed to offer such balanced Desktop PC for gaming at a good price.</p>
